rComments: Best Professor ive ever had at Utm. Actually makes me want to come to lecture, very knowledgeable and approachable. Tim's the man.

He is very inconsistent, will tell you something in class then expect something else later that week. Sometimes will not even mention an assignment then randomly expects the entire class to somehow magically know about it. I haven't really learned much, its all very vague. He skips from point to point on his horrible website. Very frustrating!

He's very accommodating, funny, and fair. He's an incredible public speaker. Listening to his lecture is like music to my ears, because he's always so informative. I've always wanted to be able to speak like him, and be thorough like he is when he's on TV. He's so nice to his students too. This prof rocks.
